(5, 1, '2014-04-28 23:02:20', '2014-04-28 23:02:20', 'James, born Feb. 16, 1869, died Oct. 26, 1934. Married Jane Arbuthnot, born Mar. 2, 1870, died Nov. 13, 1946. The relationship was stormy at times. They lived for a time in a house on a small farm east of the land Jim later bought, and in Russell Twp. Jim refused to move to his new house when he bought the larger farm, so Jane had the boys move the furniture when he was away, so that when he returned to the small house, it was empty. The larger farm was later willed to George by James, a condition of the will being that Jane was to have a home there as long as she lived.', 'James Thompson', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'james-thompson', '', '', '2014-04-29 15:12:17', '2014-04-29 15:12:17', '', 0, 'http://thompsons.plansmash.com/tree/?p=5', 0, 'post', '', 0),
