(221, 1, '2011-02-11 12:27:04', '2011-02-11 17:27:04', 'Shawn got a call from Kienan Kennedy, Nigel''s principal, telling him Nigel was suspended again. He told Shawn that Nigel punched another student in the school yard and got very angry. Nigel was using bad language and also wasn''t suppose to be outside in the first place. Kienan told Shawn that Nigel''s temper escalates and gets him into more trouble.\r\n\r\nKienan told Shawn he tried to get a hold of Mary but there was no answer. Shawn told Kienan to try Loree and he if he can''t get a hold of her to call Shawn back and he will call Margaret. Shawn didn''t want the school to call Margaret because Mary wasn''t talking to her and Shawn didn''t want the school to get in between them.', 'Call from Central Public School', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-central-public-school-2', '', '', '2011-02-12 10:49:13', '2011-02-12 15:49:13', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=221', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(306, 1, '2011-06-12 15:45:23', '2011-06-12 20:45:23', 'Called Mary and asked her if we can meet for 30 minutes to talk about Nigel. I had a few stuff to talk to her about. She said she didn''t want to meet with me. I said I just wanted to have a longer conversation than usual but she still said she couldn''t.\r\n\r\nI talk to her about it over the phone. I told her I wanted to see Nigel more during the summer and said I wanted to see him for a week at a time. She agreed for the month of July but she said that because I had him for the first two weeks of August that we should return to "normal". \r\n\r\nI talked to her about her bringing Nigel to the dentist and she agreed to. I will send her the dentist name and number. I told her I would pay for it. \r\n\r\nI asked her how was Nigel getting to and from school and she said it was a van that was picking him up and dropping him off. She said all the kids took a van and that Nigel had friends in his van. \r\n\r\nWe talked about CHEO and she said she would give me the number and the name of who she talked to. She told me that CHEO did follow ups with children but I told her Dr. Kirtsman didn''t think they did. \r\n\r\nI asked her about splitting the picking and dropping Nigel off and she said that her lawyer told her that because I moved away from Nigel''s home town it was my responsibility for transportation. I reminded her they we all moved together to Aylmer and that it was her who took Nigel away from me. But she said that she took him back to his birth place. She was getting upset and I told her that we will discuss it in mediation. I also asked her to bring in her papers next week to the court house to get this started as soon as possible. \r\n\r\nShe asked me when I was going to drop Nigel and I asked her when she would like him back. She said she would like him back now.', 'Conversation with Mary about Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'conversation-with-mary-about-nigel', '', '', '2011-06-12 17:26:41', '2011-06-12 22:26:41', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=306', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(305, 1, '2011-06-12 16:15:13', '2011-06-12 21:15:13', 'I dropped Nigel off around 4:00pm. Mary was waiting at the door for us. \r\n\r\nShe gave me the information for the contact at CHEO along with the date of Nigel''s appointment and the name of the doctor he is meeting with. \r\n\r\nI told her that Nigel got a hair cut and that the bugs were attaching him and going in his hair. She looked at his bug bits in his neck and asked if I put repellent on him. I told her we did but it didn''t seem to work. Told her if was the black flies and that we will try something different next time. \r\n\r\nI told her that I gave her the information about my health insurance so she can show Walmart to prove that Nigel was covered. She said they made a mistake and that he was covered but she had to pay the deductible before it started kicking in. \r\n\r\nI told her that I would send her a calendar for July. \r\n\r\nI told her I was in Cornwall on the weekend and that I would like to see Nigel on Sunday for father''s day. She said she was going to ask me if I wanted him but forgot..... \r\n\r\nI asked her to let me know when she got a new phone number.', 'Dropping Nigel off', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dropping-nigel-off-2', '', '', '2011-06-12 17:27:05', '2011-06-12 22:27:05', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=305', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(304, 1, '2011-06-09 12:36:32', '2011-06-09 17:36:32', 'I finally got a hold of Mary. I asked her how the meeting at CHEO went and she said good. She said CHEO can began seeing Nigel in August. I asked her to said me the contact for me to talk to the same person she spoke with. She agreed to email me the information because she "finally got a business card".\n\nI asked her where Nigel was when she was working and she said he stayed at home with Chris. I told her I wanted to talk to Nigel at night and I needed to be able to call him when I wanted to. She told me she was getting a new phone number because she switched to Cogeco and they were suppose to install the phone line today. I told her I wanted the number as soon as she got it.\n\nI told her her I had the afternoon off tomorrow and I''d be able to pick Nigel up after school. So she said I could pick him at 2:30', 'Finally talk to Mary', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '303-revision', '', '', '2011-06-09 12:36:32', '2011-06-09 17:36:32', '', 303, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=304', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(314, 1, '2011-07-19 10:17:52', '2011-07-19 15:17:52', 'Mary sent me a txt this morning to ask me when I would be picking him up today. She said she forgot. I asked her when the appointment was for Nigel''s wart removal. She replied "We go next week". I asked her if they went today and she replied "We couldn''t". I asked her "why not?" and I''m still waiting for a reply....', 'Nigel wart removal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nigel-wart-removal', '', '', '2011-07-19 10:17:52', '2011-07-19 15:17:52', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=314', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(298, 1, '2011-06-06 14:44:09', '2011-06-06 19:44:09', 'Mary went to CHEO for an appointment to talk about getting Nigel assessed by their out reach program. I asked Mary to give me the contact information for the caseworker but instead she gave me the URL for their website. http://stopandlisten.ca/\n\nI will call her at 6:00PM tonight to see how it went.', 'Mary''s visit to CHEO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marys-visit-to-cheo', '', '', '2011-06-06 14:44:09', '2011-06-06 19:44:09', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=298', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(299, 1, '2011-05-25 00:30:50', '2011-05-25 05:30:50', 'I kept calling Mary''s cell phone and i kept getting a busy signal. I sent her an email asking her to call me. She talk me that she was using a different cell phone but didn''t have many minutes on it. She said she would call me from work.', 'Cell phone - disconnected', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cell-phone-disconnected', '', '', '2011-05-25 00:30:50', '2011-05-25 05:30:50', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=299', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(300, 1, '2011-05-29 15:40:55', '2011-05-29 20:40:55', 'Mary gave me her new phone number her new phone number. (613) 662-4942.', 'Mary''s new cell number', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marys-new-cell-number', '', '', '2011-05-29 15:40:55', '2011-05-29 20:40:55', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=300', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2011-05-28 15:00:00', '2011-05-28 20:00:00', 'I went to drop Nigel off but I didn''t have a phone number to contact Mary to let her know I was coming. She finally got a hold of me and I told her I was going to drop Nigel off right away. When we got there we waited outside for about 5 minutes but she never came. Someone let us into the building and we went to her apartment door. There was a lite smell of weed but when she opened the door it didn''t smell like that in her apartment. She was shocked to see us and asked Nigel how he got in. We told her someone let us in. I told her we were waiting out there and she asked me why didn''t call the number back that called me. I told her I didn''t know that was her new phone number.', 'Dropping Nigel off', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dropping-nigel-off', '', '', '2011-06-06 15:04:34', '2011-06-06 20:04:34', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=301', 0, 'post', '', 0),
