(48, 1, '2010-12-28 17:30:00', '2010-12-28 22:30:00', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEmailed and called Mary to tell her I''m going to pick up Nigel on Dec 29. When I talked to her she sounded high. Her speech was rapid and she talked a lot about Nigel’s broken DS gaming system.  Which is very unlike her usual character. Mary approved of me picking Nigel up early.', 'Picking up Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'picking-up-nigel', '', '', '2011-02-04 15:55:54', '2011-02-04 20:55:54', '', 0, 'http://plansmash.com/blog/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
