(50, 1, '2010-12-28 17:45:07', '2010-12-28 22:45:07', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTold Margaret I was going to file a court order. Also told her I was going to pick up Nigel the next day and I was going to keep him until the court date. Explained to her that he was safer in my custody than in his mother’s care. Promised that I would not keep him from seeing his grandparents and their family. Margaret asked that I leave hers and Bill’s name off the legal papers and that I don’t tell Mary that I talked to her parents about her drug use.', 'Called Hyatts at home and spoke to Margaret', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'called-hyatts-at-home-and-spoke-to-margaret', '', '', '2011-02-04 16:00:15', '2011-02-04 21:00:15', '', 0, 'http://plansmash.com/blog/?p=50', 0, 'post', '', 0),
