(240, 1, '2011-02-14 15:22:40', '2011-02-14 20:22:40', 'Shawn tried calling the doctor 4 times (9:30, 13:20, 14:30 and 15:15) and finally go a hold of someone on the fourth time.\r\n\r\nShawn called doctor Kirtsman''s office to discuss Nigel and his health and behaviour issues. Spoke to the receptionist and left my number with her. She told me that the doctor will be away for most of March and she could only book an appointment with me near the end of March. Shawn said he would like to speak to her sooner than that and he was willing to have a conversation over the phone or even meet her in Montreal, seeing as though the doctor and him both live in Montreal. \r\n\r\nThe receptionist said that she would call him back after she spoke with the doctor. ', 'Call to doctor Kirtsman', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-doctor-kirtsman', '', '', '2011-02-14 15:24:06', '2011-02-14 20:24:06', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=240', 0, 'post', '', 0),
