(86, 1, '2011-02-06 16:01:47', '2011-02-06 21:01:47', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Constable Dupuis</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWent to the police to speak with Constable Dupuis. I asked him what would happen if I keep Nigel and refused to return him. Told him that Mary and I had no legal papers and that Nigel''s been living with her since 2006. I told him that I was going to fill court papers for custody and have her served. Constable Dupuis told me that she couldn''t take him back but that I couldn''t deny her access. He opened a report and took down all our information. He told me that Mary could call the Montreal police and have them come check on me but they couldn''t do anything unless Nigel was in danger.', 'Cornwall Police station Part 2', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '81-revision-2', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:01:47', '2011-02-06 21:01:47', '', 81, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=86', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
