(94, 1, '2010-12-30 15:00:58', '2010-12-30 20:00:58', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Witness for Shawn: Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n	<li>Witness for Mary: Unknown</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNigel: with maternal grandparents\r\n\r\nMary states that she tried calling Shawn earlier this afternoon but he did not answer. Shawn says he did not recognize the number, but will now put her home phone in his cell phone.\r\n\r\nShawn phoned Mary to ask her what she would think about him taking Nigel on a permanent basis. She said that she did not think it was a good idea because Nigel has trouble adjusting to change.\r\n\r\nMary then asked Shawn if he had received his government prescription card, because her dad had gotten his. Shawn answered that it was in the mail.\r\n\r\nShawn redirected the conversation back to the main topic saying that things are not looking so good and that Nigel does not look happy and throws fits every time before he has to go home. Shawn continues to tell her that he asks to go to his grandmother’s all the time instead of going home. Shawn says that Nigel says he doesn’t like Chris (mother’s boyfriend) Mary says that he says that he does not want to come with Shawn either, but makes no claims as of why.\r\n\r\nMary starts to cry and say that Shawn has not right to do this. Shawn says that he is worried, because Nigel has been saying that Mary’s mother wants to take him away from her and keep them apart. Shawn explains that this kind of talk is scary for him (Shawn) and says that they both need to get a final agreement on paper.\r\n\r\nMary claimed that the issue with her mother had been resolved though later to find out they have not spoken since the fight they had on the evening of December 28<sup>th. </sup>\r\n\r\nMary suggests getting something from Shoppers Drug Mart. Shawn says he wants some thing done in the courts to ensure it is legal. Mary claims once again that Shawn can’t do this.\r\n\r\nShawn also states that he has noticed that Nigel is not as well taken care of , he is dirty, he does not brush his teeth and Shawn is worried about his welfare. He explains that Nigel does not like her boyfriend and that Nigel never wants to go home. Shawn says to her not to do anything rational and to call him once she has thought about it.\r\n\r\nShawn states that he is not bringing him back on Sunday because he is worried for his safety. Mary said that he had no right and she would call the police. Shawn told her that because nothing legal was in place that it is not kidnapping unless he denied her access to him. Shawn offered for her to come to Montreal and see Nigel.\r\n\r\nMary offered to Shawn for him to come and meet the behaviorist at school, to come to her home and look around and that she would give him the email password to see that she has been sending out CVs. Shawn stated it was not just about that but did not specify what his exact fears were.\r\n\r\n<strong>Note</strong>: No mention of drug use or her health at this point to avoid any blow up.  The court order was specifically left out so that she could be served the subpoena.', 'Call to Mary outside the courthouse', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-mary-outside-the-courthouse', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:41:55', '2011-02-06 21:41:55', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=94', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(95, 1, '2011-02-06 16:19:17', '2011-02-06 21:19:17', 'Filled the court paper at the family law clerk at the courthouse.', 'Filled the court paper at the family law clerk at the courthouse.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-2', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:19:17', '2011-02-06 21:19:17', '', 92, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=95', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(96, 1, '2010-12-30 14:30:30', '2010-12-30 19:30:30', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA discussion took place between Shendah and Shawn about whether to call Mary and let her know what is going on. It is discussed that instead of bombarding her with court proceedings it is best to see if she would willingly give Nigel up, to lessen the blow. It is planned that if she does not say yes then Shawn will continue with the serving of the subpoena by Wray.', 'Talk outside the court house', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'talk-outside-the-court-house', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:35:50', '2011-02-06 21:35:50', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=96', 0, 'post', '', 0),
