(98, 1, '2010-12-30 14:45:21', '2010-12-30 19:45:21', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompsons</li>\r\n	<li>Bill Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Witness: Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn phones Bill stating that the court order has been put in the courts and that he is going to call Mary to give her one more chance before he has her served. Bill suggests being on the road before doing so. Shawn says he would rather give her a chance to give custody amicably.', 'Car outside of courthouse talking to Bill', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'car-outside-of-courthouse-talking-to-bill', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:25:12', '2011-02-06 21:25:12', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=98', 0, 'post', '', 0),
