(105, 1, '2010-12-30 15:30:05', '2010-12-30 20:30:05', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Bill Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Loree Lalonde</li>\r\n	<li>Billy Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Billy’s Girlfriend, Raquel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNigel Thompson was out of earshot\r\n\r\n(Shawn and Shendah) We went to the Hyatt’s to pick up Nigel from skating. As we arrived they invited Shawn and Shendah in.  Shendah went in.\r\n\r\nBill stayed outside with Shawn to discuss: Shawn explained that he spoke with Mary and told him that he used Bill and Margaret as “scapegoat” when he asked Mary for custody. Shawn said he told Mary that he (Shawn) was worried because of Nigel claiming that Margaret was going to take him away and keep them away forever. Bill agreed and said “ I guess you gotta do what you gotta do”. Bill also claimed that if is his daughter was healthy then he would not be doing this if Mary was heathy.\r\n\r\nShendah and Shawn showed them the court order that had been placed. A copy was not left in their possession. Shendah and Shawn explained to them that nothing was put in about the suspected drug use since they were not going to support us in the matter and because we had no proof of the drug use. Also it was explained that Shawn put in certain facts that were observable such as weight loss and lack of finances on Mary’s behalf that was added to the court order to demonstrate the health concern.\r\n\r\nMargaret agreed with the allegations in the court order and explained this by saying “ That’s exactly it”. She was crying the whole time we were there.\r\n\r\nLoree explained that they had only met Chris Chartrand (Mary’s boyfriend) a total of 3 times. On Christmas Loree claims they only came for 45 minutes and left. They said they never saw Mary anymore.\r\n\r\nThey explained that they noticed she had lost an incredible amount of weight. Shendah said that isolation from her family is a pretty good sign of this type of behavior (drug use). Margaret explained to us that Nigel would be put in a special class in school.\r\n\r\nShendah asked Margaret if he had ever been evaluated. She said it takes over a year for him to be evaluated by the school. Shendah told her that I could get an appointment for him within a month at the Douglas. She brushed off the subject and said well I guess if you do it on a personal level.\r\n\r\nShe also mentioned to us that Nigel is to be placed in a special program at school with a behaviorist.  Shendah said that it was a sad situation for everyone. Loree said that the most important thing in this case is Nigel.  Shendah, Shawn and Nigel left.', 'Shawn and Shendah at Hyatt''s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-and-shendah-at-hyatts', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:43:31', '2011-02-06 21:43:31', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=105', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(106, 1, '2011-02-06 16:43:08', '2011-02-06 21:43:08', '<ul>\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\n	<li>Bill Hyatt</li>\n	<li>Loree Lalonde</li>\n	<li>Billy Hyatt</li>\n	<li>Billy’s Girlfriend, Raquel</li>\n</ul>\nNigel Thompson was out of earshot', 'Shawn and Shendah at Hyatt''s', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '105-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:43:08', '2011-02-06 21:43:08', '', 105, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=106', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(107, 1, '2010-12-30 16:30:49', '2010-12-30 21:30:49', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Wray Coleman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShendah stayed in the care with Nigel\r\n\r\nShawn delivered the court order to be subpoenaed to Mary the next day. A description was given and a picture was shown of her. Wray Coleman said he would bill Shawn. Shawn told Wray that he thought Mary and her boyfriend were using drugs. Wray than asked for the boyfriend’s name but did not seem to recognize it.', 'Meeting with Investigator', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'meeting-with-investigator', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:44:49', '2011-02-06 21:44:49', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=107', 0, 'post', '', 0),
