(109, 1, '2010-12-30 16:30:04', '2010-12-30 21:30:04', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNigel started to cry in the car about the argument that his mother and grandmother had had. Nigel told Shendah that he would call his mother when he got to Montreal and tell her that his grandmother had apologized. Shendah explained to Nigel that sometimes when people are angry they say things they don’t mean, but apologize have to come from the person. I told him that everything would be all right between the two.', 'Wait in car', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wait-in-car', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:45:48', '2011-02-06 21:45:48', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=109', 0, 'post', '', 0),
