(111, 1, '2010-12-30 17:00:04', '2010-12-30 22:00:04', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn and Shendah asked Nigel if he wanted to spend a few more days with us and he said yes. We then asked him if he would be interested in living with us and he said “Oh no, not living”. We asked Nigel why and he told us because it would make his mother sad and she wouldn’t want that. Shawn then asked what he wanted, and Nigel said he would like to live with Shawn and Sl. Shawn and Shendah stated that they would look into it. No further discussion had taken place on the matter with Nigel not to confuse him.', 'Drive back to Montreal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'drive-back-to-montreal', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:46:52', '2011-02-06 21:46:52', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=111', 0, 'post', '', 0),
