(113, 1, '2011-02-06 16:47:54', '2011-02-06 21:47:54', '<ul>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\n</ul>\nShawn and Shendah asked Nigel if he wanted to spend a few more days with us and he said yes. We then asked him if he would be interested in living with us and he said “Oh no, not living”. We asked Nigel why and he told us because it would make his mother sad and she wouldn’t want that. Shawn then asked what he wanted, and Nigel said he would like to live with Shawn and Sl. Shawn and Shendah stated that they would look into it. No further discussion had taken place on the matter with Nigel not to confuse him.', 'Drive back to Montreal', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '111-autosave', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:47:54', '2011-02-06 21:47:54', '', 111, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=113', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(114, 1, '2010-12-31 09:15:03', '2010-12-31 14:15:03', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson (Montreal)</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt (Cornwall)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMary Hyatt called to let Shawn on his cell phone. Mary phoned to let Shawn know that she was headed to the courthouse in Cornwall to find out if Shawn was aloud to keep Nigel against her wishes. She also asked Shawn for his address in Montreal which he gave immediately. He explained that she would be receiving his address soon enough since he had a court order on it’s way.\r\n\r\nNigel spoke to his mother on speakerphone. At this point Nigel told his mother that his grandmother was very sorry. Mary did not mention the present circumstances that were going on between her and Shawn.\r\n\r\nShawn then continued his conversation with Mary away from Nigel. He explained once again that he thought it would be better that Nigel stay with him. She refused once again. She claimed to have called Shawn several times and he did not answer the phone. Shawn denies this and tells her he always answers the phone. Never once did Mary ask for Nigel right away, she asked that Shawn return him on Sunday.', 'Call from Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-mary', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:52:09', '2011-02-06 21:52:09', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(115, 1, '2011-02-06 16:52:06', '2011-02-06 21:52:06', '<ul>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson (Montreal)</li>\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\n	<li>Mary Hyatt (Cornwall)</li>\n</ul>\nMary Hyatt called to let Shawn on his cell phone. Mary phoned to let Shawn know that she was headed to the courthouse in Cornwall to find out if Shawn was aloud to keep Nigel against her wishes. She also asked Shawn for his address in Montreal which he gave immediately. He explained that she would be receiving his address soon enough since he had a court order on it’s way.\n\nNigel spoke to his mother on speakerphone. At this point Nigel told his mother that his grandmother was very sorry. Mary did not mention the present circumstances that were going on between her and Shawn.\n\nShawn then continued his conversation with Mary away from Nigel. He explained once again that he thought it would be better that Nigel stay with him. She refused once again. She claimed to have called Shawn several times and he did not answer the phone. Shawn denies this and tells her he always answers the phone. Never once did Mary ask for Nigel right away, she asked that Shawn return him on Sunday.', 'Call from Mary', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '114-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 16:52:06', '2011-02-06 21:52:06', '', 114, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=115', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
