(121, 1, '2010-12-31 14:35:39', '2010-12-31 19:35:39', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons</li>\r\n	<li>Chris Chartrand</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nChris said he did not know what to do about this situation and claimed that he found it difficult. He said that he thinks that Mary and Shawn should talk more about Nigel’s care. He said that it’s not fair that Nigel is the one telling Shawn about things that happen at school and not Mary. He claimed to have mention this to Mary and that she said she would rather not. Chris exclaimed that when his parents were divorced they talked all the time when he was younger, but that he doesn’t think they talk anymore. Chris exclaimed several times that it was just a bad situation all around (talking about the court orders and all) At this point Shendah said that the most important thing is that nigel is in a safe home. It is important that Nigel does not hear of any of this at this point since he does not understand as Chris repeated the same thing in different words to which the writer could not remember which ones. At this point Sl brought up the fact that Shendah and Shawn never bad mouth Mary and that it important that they do not bad mouth Shawn. To which Shendah confronted Chris about Nigel hearing that Chris did not like Shawn because he hurt his mommy. To which Chris defended himself and said he did not know Nigel was in the room. Shendah said that there was not reason to dislike Shawn and that statements like that are dangerous making people think that Shawn physically hurt her. Chris acknowledged that it was not a good thing. Shendah reiterated that he needs to be careful around a child of 7 who is like a sponge. Shendah and Chris went back in the house and Shendah went in the kitchen and asked whether Nigel knew that his mother and Chris were there. Shawn said yes. Shendah and Chris sat in the living room talking about mundane things such as computers. This conversation led to Chris stating he worked for J Tech in Cornwall before. Shendah asked if he was working right now and he said no that he was with a job agency called Job Zone. Shendah acknowledged knowing about the company and said that her mother was with that agency after she retired. At this point Mary and Shawn came in the living room.', 'Shendah and Chris outside smoking', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shendah-and-chris-outside-smoking', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:05:48', '2011-02-06 22:05:48', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=121', 0, 'post', '', 0),
