(126, 1, '2011-01-02 12:30:37', '2011-01-02 17:30:37', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons - witness</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Witness unknown for Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNigel Thompson  - In living room out of earshot\r\n\r\nShawn called Mary to tell her that he was not bring Nigel back and keeping Nigel in his custody until the court date on Friday, January 7<sup>th</sup>.\r\n\r\nShawn told Mary that he did not think it was safe for Nigel at her place because of Mary and Chris’ suspected drug use.\r\n\r\nShawn explained that he was suspicion of Mary’s drug use and that it has gotten worst.\r\n\r\nShawn admitted to talking to Mary’s parents and told her that her parents felt the same way as Shawn did. That they all feared that Nigel was in danger and that he was being neglected.\r\n\r\nShawn also told Mary that he heard that her boyfriend, Chris, was using crack cocaine and stealing from friends.\r\n\r\nShawn asked her to put herself in his shoes and that he was only doing what he thought was right for Nigel’s safety.\r\n\r\nMary denied using drugs and said she had not lost any weight and that she’s always weighed the same weight.\r\n\r\nMary never denied Chris drug use until Shawn made a comment about her not denying it.', 'Call to Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-mary', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:14:56', '2011-02-06 22:14:56', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=126', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(127, 1, '2011-02-06 17:14:38', '2011-02-06 22:14:38', '<ul>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\n	<li>Shendah Lyons - witness</li>\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\n	<li>Witness unknown for Mary Hyatt</li>\n</ul>\nNigel Thompson  - In living room out of earshot\n\nShawn called Mary to tell her that he was not bring Nigel back and keeping Nigel in his custody until the court date on Friday, January 7<sup>th</sup>.\n\nShawn told Mary that he did not think it was safe for Nigel at her place because of Mary and Chris’ suspected drug use.\n\nShawn explained that he was suspicion of Mary’s drug use and that it has gotten worst.\n\nShawn admitted to talking to Mary’s parents and told her that her parents felt the same way as Shawn did. That they all feared that Nigel was in danger and that he was being neglected.\n\nShawn also told Mary that he heard that her boyfriend, Chris, was using crack cocaine and stealing from friends.\n\nShawn asked her to put herself in his shoes and that he was only doing what he thought was right for Nigel’s safety.\n\nMary denied using drugs and said she had not lost any weight and that she’s always weighed the same weight.\n\nMary never denied Chris drug use until Shawn made a comment about her not denying it.', 'Call to Mary', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '126-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:14:38', '2011-02-06 22:14:38', '', 126, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=127', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2011-01-02 17:05:01', '2011-01-02 22:05:01', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons – In living room out of earshot</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson – In living room out of earshot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMargaret called to ask Shawn what Mary had to say when Shawn told her he was not going to be bringing back Nigel on Sunday. Shawn told her that Mary denied everything but nothing about Chris until Shawn mentioned it.\r\n\r\nMargaret told Shawn that Mary told Margaret to stop calling her and to leave her alone.\r\n\r\nMargaret asked Shawn when the court date was and what was it all about. Shawn told Margaret that the court date was on Friday, January 7, 2011 and that it was just a preliminary.\r\n\r\nShawn than passed the phone to Nigel so he could talk to his grandmother.\r\n\r\nNigel told Margaret that he was staying with Shawn until he starts school.\r\n\r\nNigel told Margaret that Shawn and Shendah did not have cable.\r\n\r\nNigel asked Shawn if he will be staying up late tonight and Shawn said no. Nigel passed the information to his grandmother.\r\n\r\nNigel hung up with his grandmother.', 'Call from Margaret', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-margaret', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:16:04', '2011-02-06 22:16:04', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=128', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(129, 1, '2011-02-06 17:16:02', '2011-02-06 22:16:02', '<ul>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\n	<li>Shendah Lyons – In living room out of earshot</li>\n	<li>Nigel Thompson – In living room out of earshot</li>\n</ul>\nMargaret called to ask Shawn what Mary had to say when Shawn told her he was not going to be bringing back Nigel on Sunday. Shawn told her that Mary denied everything but nothing about Chris until Shawn mentioned it.\n\nMargaret told Shawn that Mary told Margaret to stop calling her and to leave her alone.\n\nMargaret asked Shawn when the court date was and what was it all about. Shawn told Margaret that the court date was on Friday, January 7, 2011 and that it was just a preliminary.\n\nShawn than passed the phone to Nigel so he could talk to his grandmother.\n\nNigel told Margaret that he was staying with Shawn until he starts school.\n\nNigel told Margaret that Shawn and Shendah did not have cable.\n\nNigel asked Shawn if he will be staying up late tonight and Shawn said no. Nigel passed the information to his grandmother.\n\nNigel hung up with his grandmother.', 'Call from Margaret', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '128-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:16:02', '2011-02-06 22:16:02', '', 128, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=129', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(130, 1, '2011-01-03 13:45:22', '2011-01-03 18:45:22', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson (Montreal)</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt (Cornwall)</li>\r\n	<li>Shendah Lyons – In living room our of earshot</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson – In living room our of earshot</li>\r\n	<li>Witness for Mary: unknown</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn told Mary about Nigel’s hockey game tonight at 6:00PM. Shawn asked to pick up Nigel equipment and Mary agreed. Shawn than asked Mary if she would like to come to Nigel’s hockey game and Mary said she would like to go. Shawn will be picking Mary up at 5:30PM. Mary seemed pretty relaxed', 'Call to Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-mary-2', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:17:22', '2011-02-06 22:17:22', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=130', 0, 'post', '', 0),
