(132, 1, '2011-01-05 10:00:49', '2011-01-05 15:00:49', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Sandra Miller</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSandra told Shawn that Julie could not make the court date on Friday, January 7<sup>th</sup>. Shawn agreed to go to court on Friday without representation but requested a meeting the following week with Julie.\r\n\r\nEmails went back and forth and they finally agreed to meet for 45 minutes at the Cornwall courthouse on Wednesday January 12<sup>th</sup> at 1PM. Shawn agreed to bring the retainer.', 'First call to Lawyer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'first-call-to-lawyer', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:51:17', '2011-02-06 22:51:17', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=132', 0, 'post', '', 0),
