(134, 1, '2011-01-05 11:00:24', '2011-01-05 16:00:24', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Margaret Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Witness for Margaret Hyatt - unknown</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMargaret called Shawn to ask him if Nigel can join the Hyatt family for dinner at Loree Hyatt’s because Billy Hyatt was leaving the next day to go back to Alberta. Shawn approved and him and Margaret decided that 1:00PM would be a good time to pick Nigel up from the Thompsons. Shawn asked that Nigel be returned after dinner.', 'Call from Margaret', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-margaret-2', '', '', '2011-02-06 17:52:03', '2011-02-06 22:52:03', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=134', 0, 'post', '', 0),
