(137, 1, '2011-02-05 19:15:52', '2011-02-06 00:15:52', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson (Montreal)</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson (Cornwall)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn called Nigel to tell him his new bed was put together and up. Nigel was excited and asked him if was coming to get him this weekend. Shawn told him he would pick him up next weekend. Nigel said he was watching a movie but didn''t remember the name. Nigel asked Mary what the name of the movie was and she said it was Goosebumps. Shawn felt it took a log time to get an answer and that MAYBE they were lying to him. Nigel asked when did Shawn get Shendah pregnant. She replied that she was due around Nigel''s birthday. Shawn heard Mary tell Nigel something in the background and Nigel took back his question. Nigel told Shawn he was going to get off the phone to go back to his movie. Shawn told Nigel to call him back on Sunday if he wanted.', 'Call to Nigel', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-nigel', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:34:37', '2011-02-06 23:34:37', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=137', 0, 'post', '', 0),
