(139, 1, '2011-02-06 18:03:42', '2011-02-06 23:03:42', '<ul>\n	<li>Shawn Thompson (Montreal)</li>\n	<li>Nigel Thompson (Cornwall)</li>\n</ul>\nShawn called Nigel to tell him his new bed was put together and up. Nigel was excited and asked him if was coming to get him this weekend. Shawn told him he would pick him up next weekend. Nigel said he was watching a movie but didn''t remember the name. Nigel asked Mary what the name of the movie was and she said it was Goosebumps. Shawn felt it took a log time to get an answer and that MAYBE they were lying to him. Nigel asked when did Shawn get Shendah pregnant. She replied that she was due around Nigel''s birthday. Shawn heard Mary tell Nigel something in the background and Nigel took back his question. Nigel told Shawn he was going to get off the phone to go back to his movie. Shawn told Nigel to call him back on Sunday if he wanted.', 'Call to Nigel', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '137-autosave', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:03:42', '2011-02-06 23:03:42', '', 137, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=139', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(140, 1, '2011-01-05 11:30:55', '2011-01-05 16:30:55', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Diane Lamarche</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn spoke to Diane about mediation and she said we need to settle the drug use claim before going to mediation. That mediation might just go in circles before we know what we really want.\r\n\r\nDiane told Shawn that he had to file an Affidavit and bring it with him to court on Friday. Verified with the lawyer that was there. Diane said that the judge might not even look at the papers that Mary was served because they are for a different court date even though they have the same case number.', 'Back to Family Law Information Centre', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'back-to-family-law-information-centre-2', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:04:57', '2011-02-06 23:04:57', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=140', 0, 'post', '', 0),
