(142, 1, '2011-01-05 20:00:00', '2011-01-06 01:00:00', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Witness for Mary: unknown</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMary asked Shawn if she could take Nigel to see a movie on Thursday with Chris. Shawn agreed to drop Nigel off before the movie and pick him up after the movie. Mary asked Shawn to look for the times of the movie and to pick the best time. Nigel asked Mary if they could go see Tron. After looking for the rating online and found that it was rated PG, Shawn agreed\r\n\r\nMary also discussed the court date with Shawn. Mary said she was willing to split the custody with Shawn if was while to stay in Cornwall during the time he has Nigel.\r\n\r\nMary also said she was willing to take drug test to prove she wasn’t using any drugs. Shawn than asked if Chris was willing to also. Mary said he was.\r\n\r\nMary said she was willing to let someone come and inspect her place.\r\n\r\nMary and Shawn discussed Nigel medicine. Shawn told her that he would like Nigel to have a mental health evaluation.\r\n\r\nShawn also told Mary he wanted to go to Nigel’s school and speak to the staff to see firsthand what they are doing there to help Nigel. Shawn said he wanted to go alone first and after would like to go back with Mary to talk about any concerns she might have.', 'Phone conversation with Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phone-conversation-with-mary', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:05:50', '2011-02-06 23:05:50', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=142', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(143, 1, '2011-02-06 18:05:28', '2011-02-06 23:05:28', '', 'Phone conversation with Mary', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:05:28', '2011-02-06 23:05:28', '', 142, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=143', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(144, 1, '2011-01-06 11:00:04', '2011-01-06 16:00:04', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNigel called his mother to ask her about the movie in the afternoon. Shawn looked online and agreed with Mary about the 3:45 showing. Nigel talked to his mom about the movie. Shawn asked to speak to Mary after Nigel was done to finalize the arrangements. Shawn told Mary he was going to contact the school on Monday to meet with them.', 'Nigel called Mary from Shawn’s cell phone', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nigel-called-mary-from-shawn%e2%80%99s-cell-phone', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:06:28', '2011-02-06 23:06:28', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=144', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(145, 1, '2011-02-06 18:06:08', '2011-02-06 23:06:08', '', 'Nigel called Mary from Shawn’s cell phone', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '144-revision', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:06:08', '2011-02-06 23:06:08', '', 144, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=145', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2011-01-06 11:30:37', '2011-01-06 16:30:37', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Francine Fitsimmons</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSuggested by Natasha Scott, Shendah’s cousin, Shawn called Single Point Access and talked to Francine Fitsimmons about getting a mental assessment done for Nigel. Shawn told Francine that Mary and Margaret both said Nigel was seeing a behaviorist at the school. Francine said that an employee from Single Point Access working as a behaviorist named Tomas at Nigel’s school and said she’d call him to ask him if he was working with Nigel.\r\n\r\nWhile waiting for Francine to call back, Shawn asked Nigel if he was even talked to a man named Tomas at school about any problems he was having. Nigel said no and that he didn’t know a man named Tomas.\r\n\r\nFrancine called back and said that Tomas was not working with Nigel although Tomas said Nigel might be working with Sasha McQuinn (?). Shawn asked Nigel if he knew a lady at school named Sasha or Mrs. McQuinn. Nigel said he didn’t know anyone by those names.\r\n\r\nShawn told Francine he was going to call the school on Monday and talk to them then. Francine told Shawn to call her back after speaking with the school and Shawn agreed.', 'First contact with Single Point Access ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'first-contact-with-single-point-access', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:07:29', '2011-02-06 23:07:29', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=146', 0, 'post', '', 0),
