(148, 1, '2011-01-06 13:20:40', '2011-01-06 18:20:40', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Dean Stanley</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDean asked Shawn if he could meet with Nigel to ask him a few questions. Shawn agreed to go to his office and bring Nigel right away because Mary was taking Nigel to go see a movie at 3:30PM', 'Shawn called Dean Stanley at CAS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-called-dean-stanley-at-cas', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:08:25', '2011-02-06 23:08:25', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=148', 0, 'post', '', 0),
