(150, 1, '2011-01-06 13:45:32', '2011-01-06 18:45:32', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Dean Stanley</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOnce there, Dean took Nigel into a small room with a table, chairs and a kid’s game on the floor. Dean showed Shawn where they would be and asked Shawn to wait in the lobby while he asked Nigel a few questions. When they came out, Nigel was carrying a drawing of Spiderman that Dean gave him. Dean said his daughter made the drawing. On the way out Nigel told me that Dean asked him not to tell me what they talked about and I said that was ok.', 'Shawn drove Nigel to the CAS office on Boundary Road to meet with Dean', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-drove-nigel-to-the-cas-office-on-boundary-road-to-meet-with-dean', '', '', '2011-02-06 18:08:59', '2011-02-06 23:08:59', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=150', 0, 'post', '', 0),
