(154, 1, '2011-01-06 15:30:12', '2011-01-06 20:30:12', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn drove Nigel to the theater and brought him in. While they were waiting for Mary, Shawn paid for Nigel to play the racing game. Mary alone and went to buy the tickets for her and Nigel. Nigel played the racing game while Mary went to buy the tickets. Shawn waited with Nigel. Mary said she brought some snacks (Hotrods) and drinks in her purse for her and Nigel to have during the movie. Mary returned and Nigel finished his game. Mary and Nigel entered the viewing area and Shawn watched them go in. Shawn waited a few minutes and then left the theatre.', 'Shawn brought Nigel to meet Mary at the Galaxy movie theater', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-brought-nigel-to-meet-mary-at-the-galaxy-movie-theater', '', '', '2011-02-06 20:59:53', '2011-02-07 01:59:53', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=154', 0, 'post', '', 0),
