(156, 1, '2011-01-06 17:30:01', '2011-01-06 22:30:01', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn arrived early and sat down waiting by New York Fries. The movie ended and Mary and Nigel came out. Mary said Nigel lost interest in the movie. Mary bought Nigel some food because she said he wouldn’t stop asking her for food and saying he was hungry.\r\n\r\nShawn offered to drive Mary home after and she accepted.\r\n\r\nWhen Nigel and Shawn got back to Shawn’s parents, Nigel ate his dinner. Even though he had hotdog and snacks at the movies.', 'Shawn returned to the theatre to pick up Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-returned-to-the-theatre-to-pick-up-nigel', '', '', '2011-02-06 21:00:43', '2011-02-07 02:00:43', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=156', 0, 'post', '', 0),
