(158, 1, '2011-01-07 09:00:46', '2011-01-07 14:00:46', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Girl at the Family Law counter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn went to file the affidavit at the Family Law counter. The girl at the counter said Shawn had to served Mary with the Affidavit and come back to fill out a form to have the judge hear the Shawn’s case he first served Mary.', 'Shawn went to the court house to file the Affidavit', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-went-to-the-court-house-to-file-the-affidavit', '', '', '2011-02-06 21:01:17', '2011-02-07 02:01:17', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=158', 0, 'post', '', 0),
