(168, 1, '2011-01-07 10:30:41', '2011-01-07 15:30:41', 'Shawn Thompson\r\n\r\nDean Stanley\r\n\r\nShawn asked Mr. Stanley if he could give him an update on Nigel’s file. Mr. Stanley stated that he could not give him any information on the case even though Shawn was the one who called in to report his concerns. Shawn than asked if there were any advice that Mr. Stanley could give him on what to do next. Mr. Stanley said there was nothing he could say. He then told Shawn that he could only say anything if he thought Nigel was in danger.', 'Shawn called Mr. Stanley and left a message to return his called. Mr. Stanley called back shortly after.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-called-mr-stanley-and-left-a-message-to-return-his-called-mr-stanley-called-back-shortly-after', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:27:08', '2011-02-07 22:27:08', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=168', 0, 'post', '', 0),
