(172, 1, '2011-01-12 16:30:50', '2011-01-12 21:30:50', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Sara-Jane Woods</li>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMrs. Woods invited Shawn to a meeting on January 13<sup>th</sup> at 9:00AM about placing Nigel in a special class. Mary will be attending the meeting. Shawn had to ask to reschedule the meeting because he had a meeting in Ottawa in the morning. Mrs. Woods called Mary to see if she could make it in the afternoon instead.\r\n\r\nMrs. Woods called back to confirm that the meeting could be rescheduled to the afternoon at 2:30PM.', 'Call from Central Public School', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-central-public-school', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:33:18', '2011-02-07 22:33:18', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=172', 0, 'post', '', 0),
