(182, 1, '2011-01-21 16:30:49', '2011-01-21 21:30:49', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn talked to Nigel about the voice mail and told him it hurt Shawn’s feelings. Nigel said I deserve that for telling the principle about the hamster and for saying that his mother never gives him a bath. Nigel then said he didn’t want to come see if next weekend and that he was going to change his name to Nigel Chartrant. Shawn told him that he was hurting his feelings. Shawn asked to speak to Mary.\r\n\r\nShawn asked Mary why she was telling Nigel all about the CAS case and that Shawn was worried about Nigel safety at her place. Mary told Shawn she wasn’t going to lie to Nigel when he asks why the CAS guy would come to inspect their place and Nigel’s room. Shawn told her that wasn’t the best thing because she was turning Nigel against Shawn.\r\n\r\nMary said that CAS closed the case and that she’s already went for drug test and passed everything. Shawn asked what kind of test and Mary answered that they were urine test. Shawn said he would like hair samples done. Mary didn’t seem to like that request.\r\n\r\nShawn asked for permission to see the CAS file but Mary denied him. Mary said Shawn could see the closed copy of the CAS file but he could not have a copy. She said he would need a subpoena to actually get a copy. The conversation got heated…\r\n\r\nMary accused Shawn on smoking pot when they first met. Shawn denied that and told her the last time he smoked put, since his accident in 1998, was long before they met and that Shawn wasn’t able to handle being high because of his injury to his brain.\r\n\r\nShawn said they still had a court date in February and that he will see her in court. Mary brought up that Shawn use to masturbate with the door open when they lived together and that Nigel was in the apartment… Mary threatened to call the cops on Shawn because she says he posted naked pictures of her online. Shawn denies doing that although Shawn did have pictures on his computer of her. He no longer has them.', 'Shawn returns call', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shawn-returns-call', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:36:30', '2011-02-07 22:36:30', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=182', 0, 'post', '', 0),
