(186, 1, '2011-01-23 10:30:07', '2011-01-23 15:30:07', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn called Nigel at his aunts. Nigel talked about playing Mario Bros with his cousin and that she kept un-pausing the game. Nigel asked Shawn if he will see him at Nigel’s hockey game tonight and Shawn told him that he wouldn’t be able to make it because he will be in Montreal but that Shawn will see him on Friday to pick him up for the weekend. Nigel didn’t reply to that and said he had to go back to the game. Nigel told Shawn he loved him.', 'Call to Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-nigel-2', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:37:40', '2011-02-07 22:37:40', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=186', 0, 'post', '', 0),
