(188, 1, '2011-01-25 16:30:48', '2011-01-25 21:30:48', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn called Nigel and talked to him about various things. Nigel was listening to music and would put the phone close to the speaker so Shawn would hear. Nigel sounded happy.\r\n\r\nShawn asked Nigel how hockey went on Sunday and Monday and if Nigel scored any goals. Nigel said he didn’t score any. Shawn asked Nigel how he liked his new class and Nigel answered that he liked it but didn’t say much more about it.\r\n\r\nShawn told Nigel that he would be picking him up on Friday. Nigel didn’t respond negatively or positively to that.', 'Call to Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-nigel-3', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:38:15', '2011-02-07 22:38:15', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=188', 0, 'post', '', 0),
