(190, 1, '2011-01-26 09:30:17', '2011-01-26 14:30:17', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Kieran Kennedy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKieran told Shawn that Nigel got to school and threatened another boy. Nigel told the boy he was going to kill him and hit him in the face, breaking his glasses. Kieran said that Nigel was going to have to be expelled from school for 3 days because of the severity of his actions. Kieran tried to get a hold of Mary but could not get a contact her. Shawn told Kieran that he would get a hold of someone to pick Nigel up from school. Kieran and Shawn agreed to meet sometime next week to talk about Nigel’s behavior. Shawn explained that Nigel needs help at home with his mother and that Shawn would need all the help that Kieran can give him to work with Mary.\r\n\r\nShawn called Loree and spoke to Billy. Billy agreed to pick Nigel up from school.', 'Call from Mr. Kennedy - Suspension', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-mr-kennedy-suspension', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:39:17', '2011-02-07 22:39:17', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=190', 0, 'post', '', 0),
