(192, 1, '2011-01-26 10:15:24', '2011-01-26 15:15:24', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMary called Shawn to tell him she went to pick up Nigel at school. Mary said that Nigel wasn’t the one who started the fight on the bus. She said the other boy hit Nigel first and that it wasn’t the first time Nigel got in trouble because of this boy.\r\n\r\nShawn said Nigel need to see someone about his behavior. Mary said she spoke to the behaviorist at the school, Tomas, and that he wouldn’t see Nigel because of the custody battle Mary and I were going through.  Shawn said he was going to call Tomas to verify and to tell Tomas that Shawn gives his consent.\r\n\r\nMary said she was going to bring Nigel to doctor Kirtsman to get a referral for Nigel. Shawn told her to wait because he was going to call Tomas and fix that issue.\r\n\r\nMary asked Shawn if he wanted to speak to Nigel but Shawn said he was upset with him and that he would rather wait it out. Shawn said he was going to call Nigel tonight.', 'Call from Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-mary-2', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:39:59', '2011-02-07 22:39:59', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=192', 0, 'post', '', 0),
