(194, 1, '2011-01-26 10:30:08', '2011-01-26 15:30:08', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Tomas Mynarowich</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nShawn called Tomas to talk to him about the custody issue. Shawn started off by introducing himself as Nigel’s father.  Shawn explained the custody of Nigel and that it’s a verbal agreement between Shawn and Mary that they had shared custody with Mary as primary caregiver.\r\n\r\nShawn and Tomas talked about Nigel’s behavior and his problems with sharing his emotions and his violence. Shawn told Tomas that Mary put Nigel on meds since he was 3 and that Nigel was never assessed by a metal health professional.\r\n\r\nShawn explained that he would like to have Nigel assessed and that he would like to be involved in the process.\r\n\r\nShawn explained that he didn’t agree with the way Mary was raising Nigel but that all he could do was become more involved in Nigel’s life.\r\n\r\nShawn ended the conversation with telling Tomas that he gives his consent to have Nigel assessed and will be in touch with Tomas on a regular basis.', 'Call to Tomas Mynarowich', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-tomas-mynarowich', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:40:51', '2011-02-07 22:40:51', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=194', 0, 'post', '', 0),
