(208, 1, '2011-02-03 16:00:20', '2011-02-03 21:00:20', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMary called Shawn to talk about Nigel and what his doctor, Dr. Kirtsman, had to say. Mary said the doctor was worried about Nigel’s lying. Nigel lied in the doctor’s office and the doctor saw it. Mary told the doctor that she caught him in a few lies but she never notice he lied that much. Mary than said the first lie she caught him in was the lie about Shendah being pregnant, that Nigel told her when he came home after New Years. Shawn told Mary that he’s caught Nigel in many lies and that Nigel should be disciplined the same no matter how small the lie is. Mary said Nigel was always honest with her in the past and that this saw something new. She did say that he would tell her that he changed his clothes but would actually not change them and hide the clean clothes in his room. Shawn advised Mary that this was lying and that he should be disciplined for it.\r\n\r\nMary said that she spoke with both Tomas, the councilor from Nigel’s school, and Nigel’s doctor about assessments and they both recommended taking Nigel to CHEO in Ottawa. Shawn suggested looking into maybe help in Montreal also seeing as thought Shendah works at the Douglas Hospital and that Shawn lives near by. Mary agreed to look into it as well as the recommendations from Nigel’s doctor and Tomas.\r\n\r\nMary also talked about a Dr. Kon (spelling ?) but said CHEO was recommended more by both Dr. Kirtsman and Thomas.\r\n\r\nNigel has an appointment with Dr. Kirtsman on Wednesday, February 9, 2011.\r\n\r\nMary told Shawn that Nigel had a good week at school and that him and the boy he hit made up. Mary told Shawn that Nigel was no longer taking the bus to school. He was now taking a van, which has fewer children onboard. Mary says she thinks that Nigel was too busy with all the other children on the bus.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Mary shared more information about Nigel during this call than she ever has before. She was acting as if she wanted Shawn to be involved.</em></strong>', 'Call from Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-mary-3', '', '', '2011-02-07 17:50:38', '2011-02-07 22:50:38', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=208', 0, 'post', '', 0);
