(296, 1, '2011-03-13 10:37:00', '2011-03-13 15:37:00', 'Margaret called Nigel from Florida and while talking to her, he told her that they (Mary, Nigel and Chris) went to Margaret''s place while she was away they went to her place and took some chips. He didn''t talk about anything else', 'Nigel''s talk with grandma', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '295-revision', '', '', '2011-03-13 10:37:00', '2011-03-13 15:37:00', '', 295, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=296', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(212, 1, '2011-02-08 15:30:27', '2011-02-08 20:30:27', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Shawn Thompson</li>\r\n	<li>Mary Hyatt</li>\r\n	<li>Nigel Thompson</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMary called Shawn back to talk about Nigel being covered under Shawn''s health insurance plan. Mary told Shawn that when she tried to use the medical insurance card he gave her at the Wal-Mart pharmacy, they told her that Nigel wasn''t covered under Shawn''s plan. Shawn told Mary that he called SunLife insurance twice to make sure Nigel was covered and that Shawn could give Mary the card to use for Nigel''s medication. Mary said she told Wal-Mart that and they assured her that Nigel wasn''t covered under the plan. Shawn said he would look into it.\r\n\r\nThey also talked about the meeting with Nigel''s principle on February 16 at Central Public School. Mary agreed to the requested time and day. Mary asked if the school cancelled the meeting that was set up for Thursday February 10th. Shawn said he knew nothing about that meeting.\r\n\r\nMary told Shawn that Nigel didn''t go to school today because he was congested.\r\n\r\nMary told Shawn that Nigel had a hockey game on Friday and Shawn agreed to pick him up at the arena after the game. Nigel''s game is at 6PM. Shawn will be coming from Ottawa to pick Nigel up and he said he will meet Mary there. Mary agreed to bring Nigel''s weekend bag with them. Mary then asked if Shawn would like to speak to Nigel. Shawn said yes\r\n\r\nShawn talked to Nigel. Shawn told Nigel that the phone was echoing and Nigel told him, he heard it also. Shawn asked him if he really did and Nigel told him he was joking. Shawn told him that that was lying and that Shawn didn''t like it when Nigel lied. Nigel was hard to hear over the phone with the echo. Nigel talked about the glass he broke when he hit the other boy and that the glasses were fixed and that Shawn wouldn''t have to pay for them. Shawn said they could talk about that when they see each other. Shawn asked Nigel about his cold and N