(247, 1, '2011-02-15 12:00:42', '2011-02-15 17:00:42', 'I got a call from Janet Gellately, interim Vice Principle, to tell me Nigel got in trouble twice already today and that if it happened again he was going to be suspended. \r\n\r\nJanet told me that she also contacted Mary about these incidents.\r\n\r\nI asked her to send him the details in an email and thanked her for calling him to inform him. ', 'Call from Nigel''s School', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-nigels-school', '', '', '2011-02-15 20:00:07', '2011-02-16 01:00:07', '', 0, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=247', 0, 'post', '', 0),
