(282, 1, '2011-02-22 16:29:44', '2011-02-22 21:29:44', 'I finally got a call from Nigel. I asked him how he was doing and what he''s been doing. I told him I have been trying to call him for a week. He told me he''s been out of the house all weekend but wasn''t sure where he was. \r\n\r\nI asked to speak with Mary. I asked her why she hasn''t been returning my calls since Wednesday and she said her and Nigel have been away during the day. I asked her if she was out all night and she said they were home in the evenings. I commented on her not getting my messages until last night? And asked her why she didn''t return them when she got them last night. She didn''t answer my question. She told me that she had an appointment tomorrow morning to see about the "Snap" program with Nigel tomorrow morning. I told her I was going to go with her and she said I didn''t need to go because it was just registration. \r\n\r\nShe also said she was meeting with Thomas at 2:00PM to visit the Day Treatment Centre. I told her I wanted to be there also and she said that Thomas wanted her to be there alone because she would feel more comfortable. ', 'Call from Nigel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-nigel', '', '', '2011-02-22 16:47:50', '2011-02-22 21:47:50', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=282', 0, 'post', '', 0),
