(286, 1, '2011-02-22 17:08:55', '2011-02-22 22:08:55', 'I received a return call from Thomas. I asked him about the meeting with Mary at 2:00PM. He told me that it wasn''t a meeting between them but a tour of the Day Treatment Centre with Dawn and Mary. I told him I wanted to be included in that and asked him why I wasn''t invited to the tour. Thomas said that Mary requested to go on tour alone and that he set up a tour just for her. He said he had to respect her decision. I told him I wanted to be involved about all decision involving my son. He agreed to set up a meeting with Dawn and me and said he''d try to do it for tomorrow. I asked him about the SNAP program and he said he didn''t know anything about it. I told him that Nigel was suspended from school again tomorrow for threats and swearing.\r\n\r\nI told him that Dr. Kirtsman wanted to meet with him, Mary and I to talk about Nigel and what was best for him. Thomas said why don''t Mary, him and I meet and Mary and I can report back what was discussed to the doctor. I told him that I sent Kirtsman the information for the program at the Douglas, in Montreal, and she was to contact them. I told him that we (Shendah) can get Nigel assessed right away and that CHEO usually have a waiting list. He agreed that Nigel needed to be assessed as soon as possible. ', 'Call from Thomas', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-thomas', '', '', '2011-02-22 17:08:55', '2011-02-22 22:08:55', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=286', 0, 'post', '', 0),
