(288, 1, '2011-02-22 16:45:58', '2011-02-22 21:45:58', 'I called Mary back to tell her I wanted to go with her to visit the Day Treatment Centre at 2:00PM. I told her I didn''t want her making any decisions having to do with my son without me. She told me she wasn''t comfortable with me around all the time and that she would much rather visit alone. She said she would not make any decisions and that it was just to visit the Centre. She said that I have done some bad things to her in the past and that she''s not comfortable having me around. I told her to get over herself and that I need to be around for Nigel''s wellbeing. I agreed to not go to the visit if Mary would write me an email stating that she will not make any decisions about the Centre without me. She agreed to write the email. She asked for one from me stating the same. I said I would but I have never made a decision concerning Nigel without talking to her about it. I stated that I met with Dr. Kirtsman on Wednesday and called her right after to talk to her and that she didn''t return my calls until today (Tuesday).\r\n\r\nI told her I was going to the S.N.AP. registration with her tomorrow and she told me where it was and that it was at 11:00AM.', 'Call back to Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-back-to-mary', '', '', '2011-02-22 17:22:10', '2011-02-22 22:22:10', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=288', 0, 'post', '', 0),
