(290, 1, '2011-02-22 18:15:21', '2011-02-22 23:15:21', 'I called Mary and asked her about CHEO. I don''t remember what she said. She didn''t say much about the call.\r\n\r\nI told Mary that we need to work together and get over any problems we have. I told her that she has to feel comfortable around me because she''s stuck with me for the rest of Nigel''s life. I told her I would do anything to convince her she could trust me and that I only called CAS because I was very worried about Nigel. I told her that I didn''t want full custody and that I don''t think pull him away from his mother would be such a good thing to do right now. She said she thought that if Nigel were to come to the hospital in Montreal that I would use it against her in custody battle. I advised her that I wouldn''t and that I just want what''s best for him. Mary was also worried that OHIP wouldn''t pay for it and I told her the hospital would bill OHIP directly and that she has nothing to worry about. I also told her that the Douglas could see Nigel right away.\r\n\r\nI told her I was very worried about her and Nigel this weekend and that I called the school first thing this morning to make sure Nigel was there. I told her I was about to show up at her place with the cops if Nigel wasn''t at school today. She told me she tried to get Nigel out of the house all weekend to keep him occupied. And she didn''t check her email or her phone at all when she got home. I told her that I know Chris doesn''t like me but he should have told her I called everyday and that he should have told her about it. I told her that Chris told Shendah that he thought it was weird that her and I didn''t talk much. I told her that I was willing to go to counselling with her to work though our problems. I need her to trust me and to work with me for Nigel''s wellbeing.\r\n\r\nShe said that Dr. Kirtsman suggested Dr. Kon(?) in Cornwall to do the full assessment but I told her that Kirtsman didn''t talk about a Dr. Kon(?) with me. All she talked to me about was Dr. Laplante and CHEO. She said she was going to call the doctor tomorrow and talk to her about the assessment. I told her to ask the doctor about the information I sent and if she was able to contact the Douglas.\r\n\r\nI talked to Nigel and said good night to him. He told me that he was worried about me and his mom fighting and I told him not to worry about that and that her and I will work it out. He said he remembers the big fight we had when she left me. I told him we didn''t have a big fight and that he was too young to remember that. (He was 2.5 years old at the time). He told me he was going to call me in the morning.', 'Call to Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-to-mary-9', '', '', '2011-02-22 18:26:46', '2011-02-22 23:26:46', '', 0, 'http://shawn-pc/blog/?p=290', 0, 'post', '', 0),
