(308, 1, '2011-06-12 17:24:13', '2011-06-12 22:24:13', 'I dropped Nigel off around 4:00pm. Mary was waiting at the door for us. \n\nShe gave me the information for the contact at CHEO along with the date of Nigel''s appointment and the name of the doctor he is meeting with. \n\nI told her that Nigel got a hair cut and that the bugs were attaching him and going in his hair. She looked at his bug bits in his neck and asked if I put repellent on him. I told her we did but it didn''t seem to work. Told her if was the black flies and that we will try something different next time. \n\nI told her that I gave her the information about my health insurance so she can show Walmart to prove that Nigel was covered. She said they made a mistake and that he was covered but she had to pay the deductible before it started kicking in. \n\nI told her that I would send her a calendar for July. \n\nI told her I was in Cornwall on the weekend and that I would like to see Nigel on Sunday for father''s day. She said she was going to ask me if I wanted him but forgot..... \n\nI asked her to let me know when she got a new phone number.', 'Dropping Nigel off', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '305-revision', '', '', '2011-06-12 17:24:13', '2011-06-12 22:24:13', '', 305, 'http://home.plansmash.com/blog/?p=308', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(309, 1, '2011-06-15 09:38:07', '2011-06-15 14:38:07', 'Received a call from Kelly at SNAP. She told me that there was more interview to have with Mary and I and that they were trying to get a hold of Mary to schedule an appointment but they didn''t have a working phone number. I gave them Chris'' cell number and told her she can try that number. She said that they will get a hold of Mary and call me back to let me know when the appointment was booked for.', 'Call from Kelly at SNAP', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-kelly-at-snap', '', '', '2011-06-15 09:38:07', '2011-06-15 14:38:07', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=309', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(310, 1, '2011-06-17 17:00:06', '2011-06-17 22:00:06', 'Mary called to tell me she brought Nigel to the dentist and that he had to return because the 2 filling he got last year fell out and that they will also be putting a coat on his teeth. She said he was very good while at the dentist. \n\nShe also said she but more minutes on her phone and got a plan that allows her free in coming calls and free after 7PM. It''s the same number as before and it''s still on my my10. \n\nI told her that I will be picking Nigel up on Sunday before lunch and bringing him back after dinner.', 'Nigel dentist', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nigel-dentist', '', '', '2011-06-17 17:00:06', '2011-06-17 22:00:06', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=310', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(311, 1, '2011-06-19 09:29:36', '2011-06-19 14:29:36', 'I picked up Nigel for father''s day at 10am. Nigel was wearing the "shut up and fish" hat. I told Mary to keep the hat and that I was going to get him a new hat. She said kid hats doesn''t fit him as if all grown up hats have bad sayings on them. \n\nNigel just had his bath. I think he was sleeping when I called Mary at 9:30am. Nigel said he didn''t have breakfast. \n\nTold Mary that I will be bringing him back after dinner.', 'Pick up Nigel - fathers day', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pick-up-nigel-fathers-day', '', '', '2011-06-19 09:29:36', '2011-06-19 14:29:36', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=311', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(312, 1, '2011-07-07 13:01:43', '2011-07-07 18:01:43', 'Meet with Mary at the SNAP office. They gave us a copy of Nigel''s objectives for the program and asked us to sign them. They asked us our availability during the week and I told them the only day I wasn''t available during the week was Tuesday. Mary told them she had to work at 3 during the day so it would have to be early during the day. After the meeting Mary and I thought maybe we should wait for the next round of SNAP to enroll Nigel in the program. They told us the second round of SNAP will probably start in October. \n\nI than took Nigel for the week and offered Mary a ride home. She said she was going to the mall so she declined.', 'Meeting at SNAP', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'meeting-at-snap', '', '', '2011-07-07 13:01:43', '2011-07-07 18:01:43', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=312', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(313, 1, '2011-07-07 13:06:27', '2011-07-07 18:06:27', 'Mary called and she said the people from SNAP called her and said that they will be holding the sessions on Tuesday at 4PM. We discussed that we both agreed it would be better to wait for the second round of session to bring Nigel. Mary said she will notify them of our decision.', 'Call from Mary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'call-from-mary-7', '', '', '2011-07-07 13:06:27', '2011-07-07 18:06:27', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=313', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(315, 1, '2011-07-19 10:00:31', '2011-07-19 15:00:31', 'Mary sent me a txt this morning to ask me when I would be picking him up today. She said she forgot. I asked her when the appointment was for Nigel''s wart removal. She replied "We go next week". I asked her if they went today and she replied "We couldn''t". I asked her "why not?" and I''m still waiting for a reply....\n\n', 'Nigel wart removal', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '314-revision', '', '', '2011-07-19 10:00:31', '2011-07-19 15:00:31', '', 314, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=315', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(316, 1, '2011-08-17 14:01:32', '2011-08-17 19:01:32', 'I talked to Della McCully from CHEO. Della told me that they only deal with the primary care giver and expect that person to pass on the information to the other parent. I told her that Mary has a tendency of keeping thing from me and that both of us have a different way of dealing with Nigel. We made plans to for me to meet with Jennifer Munroe at 12:45 the day of Nigel''s appointment, Thursday August 25, 2011. Jennifer told me that she will be giving me questionnaires to fill out and explain to me what their services are. I asked them if they were only an ADHD client or if they specialized in other behaviors. She said they also specialized in aggression also. I told them I had a copy of the Conners 3 - Parent Questionnaires and bring it with me on Thursday. She said that would be good. She said if I''m not sure of any question, to skip it and we could go over it together. She said if I wasn''t sure if Nigel was a 2 or 3, to skip it and she will review it with me. ', 'Phone Call from CHEO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phone-call-from-cheo', '', '', '2011-08-17 14:04:54', '2011-08-17 19:04:54', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=316', 0, 'post', '', 0),
