(335, 1, '2012-01-16 12:30:08', '2012-01-16 17:30:08', 'Nigel had a very productive morning. He was able to finish all his work! He also had no behaviours (only needed redirection when it came to other classmates) Nigel did engage with another classmate but once the classmate was removed, Nigel was able to resume classwork!\r\n\r\nChanelle\r\n\r\n*Would it be possible to initial the comm book after reading it so I know it''s being given to you. Thank you!\r\n\r\nMH signed', 'Day Treatment Book, Jan 16, 2012', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'day-treatment-book-jan-16-2012', '', '', '2012-03-20 12:59:18', '2012-03-20 17:59:18', '', 0, 'http://www.plansmash.com/7468/?p=335', 0, 'post', '', 0),
